            "headline": "XRP's investor demand wanes as market stalls. Can it defend $2? XRP rallied 600% in 2024-25, with a 490% increase in daily active addresses. $1B in whales' sell-off. $30B inflow in 6 mos. XRP's $2 support faces retests, bullish signs in lower timeframes. Potential rally to $2.13; bearish trend on higher time frame with $1.07 target..isnanListed market value. Readers advised to research before investing.",
